'''Duracrete''' was a synthetic [[stone]] product<ref name="SWTVE" /> used to make buildings. It was eaten by the [[duracrete slug]]s native to the [[planet]] [[Coruscant]].<ref name="AEYNTK" /> The ceiling of [[Docking Bay 94]] on [[Tatooine]] was also made of duracrete.<ref name="ANH" />

